<lb n="0040b02" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0040b0201"><l>又前觀智身</l><l>自心流<note n="0040048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婀＝阿【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0040048"><lem wit="【大】">婀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">阿</rdg></app>字</l>
<lb n="0040b03" ed="T"/><l>面前成月輪</l><l>即出生金剛</l>
<lb n="0040b04" ed="T"/><l>五峯流猛焰</l><l>生三悅我是</l>
<lb n="0040b05" ed="T"/><l>又<note n="0040049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">丈於＝大誓【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0040049"><lem wit="【大】">丈於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">大誓</rdg></app>世尊</l><l>即召滿空佛</l>
<lb n="0040b06" ed="T"/><l>入金剛鎖悅</l><l>又稱明顯言</l>
<lb n="0040b07" ed="T"/><l>金剛即變成</l><l>吽迦囉金剛</l>
<lb n="0040b08" ed="T"/><l>暴怒處月輪</l><l>身流火光聚</l>
<lb n="0040b09" ed="T"/><l>遍體玄青色</l><l>大自在天王</l>
<lb n="0040b10" ed="T"/><l>妃烏摩為座</l><l>歷然分明見</l>
<lb n="0040b11" ed="T"/><l>即四印加持</l><l>又示羯摩印</l>
<lb n="0040b12" ed="T"/><l>滿月已五灌</l><l>寶鬘甲拍等</l>
<lb n="0040b13" ed="T"/><l>施內外供養</l><l>自住薩埵身</l>
<lb n="0040b14" ed="T"/><l>扭擲金剛杵</l><l>震動大千界</l>
<lb n="0040b15" ed="T"/><l>誦百八名讚</l><l>都請諸<note n="0040050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聖賢＝聖等【甲】，賢聖【丙】</note><note n="0040050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聖賢＝聖等【甲】，＝賢聖【丙】</note><app n="0040050"><lem wit="【大】">聖賢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">聖等</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">賢聖</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0040b16" ed="T"/><l>鉤召索引入</l><l>鎖<note n="0040051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">止＝上【明】</note><app n="0040051"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上</rdg></app>鈴悅喜</l>
<lb n="0040b17" ed="T"/><l>四明召智身</l><l>入自體無二</l>
<lb n="0040b18" ed="T"/><l>又四加示誓</l><l>滿月已五灌</l>
<lb n="0040b19" ed="T"/><l>寶鬘甲<note n="0040052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拍＝怕【甲】</note><app n="0040052"><lem wit="【大】">拍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">怕</rdg></app>已</l><l>又陳內外供</l>
<lb n="0040b20" ed="T"/><l>即起平身立</l><l>舉右足左旋</l>
<lb n="0040b21" ed="T"/><l>攝彼傲慢者</l><l>大自在欲王</l>
<lb n="0040b22" ed="T"/><l>撲至於地已</l><l>定按於彼頂</l>
<lb n="0040b23" ed="T"/><l>慧踐彼王妃</l><l>烏摩乳房上</l>
<lb n="0040b24" ed="T"/><l>摧彼我慢故</l><l>以足加於頂</l>
<lb n="0040b25" ed="T"/><l>被害殞此已</l><l>灰嚴界成佛</l>
<lb n="0040b26" ed="T"/><l>住是三昧時</l><l>極力頻<note n="0040053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">身＝申【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0040053"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">申</rdg></app><note n="0040054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蹋＝踰【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040054"><lem wit="【大】">蹋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">踰</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0040b27" ed="T"/><l>或身掉出<note n="0040055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">污＝汗【甲】</note><app n="0040055"><lem wit="【大】">污</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">汗</rdg></app></l><l>當知<note n="0040056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尊＝身【甲】</note><app n="0040056"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">身</rdg></app>攝受</l>
<lb n="0040b28" ed="T"/><l>定慧金剛拳</l><l>二地<note n="0040057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">結＝縛【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040057"><lem wit="【大】">結</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">縛</rdg></app>風<note n="0040058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">背＝音【明】，怖【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0040058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">背＝音【明】，＝怖【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040058"><lem wit="【大】">背</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">音</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">怖</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0040b29" ed="T"/><l><note n="0040059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">循＝脩【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040059"><lem wit="【大】">循</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【丙】">脩</rdg></app>身觀相好</l><l>歷然見如前</l>
<pb n="0040c" xml:id="T21.1209.0040c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0040c01" ed="T"/><l>旋時誦足鉤</l></lg><p xml:id="pT21p0040c0106" rend="inline">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0040c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0040c0201" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0040060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引迦引那引羯＝播引娜引迦【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040060"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>那<note place="inline">引</note>羯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">播引娜引迦</rdg></app>哩灑<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0040061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">庾＝喻【甲】，喻引【丙】</note><note n="0040061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">庾＝喻【甲】，＝喻引【丙】</note><app n="0040061"><lem wit="【大】">庾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">喻</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">喻引</rdg></app>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吽
<lb n="0040c03" ed="T"/><note place="inline"><note n="0040062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">短＋（聲）【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0040062"><lem wit="【大】">短</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">短聲</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0040c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0040c0401"><note n="0040063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">步＝佛【明】</note><app n="0040063"><lem wit="【大】">步</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛</rdg></app>蹋時真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0040c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0040c0501" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0040064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0040064"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0040065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0040065"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日<note n="0040066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0040066"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0040067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麼＝摩【甲】</note><app n="0040067"><lem wit="【大】">麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">摩</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0040068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">半＋（音）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0040068"><lem wit="【大】">半</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">半音</rdg></app></note>吽<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0040062"><lem wit="【大】">短</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">短聲</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0040c06" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0040c0601"><l>又見自心月</l><l>金剛具五峯</l>
<lb n="0040c07" ed="T"/><l>中有所持明</l><l>流射金剛火</l>
<lb n="0040c08" ed="T"/><l>住是<note n="0040069" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝火【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040069"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">火</rdg></app>三昧</l><l>持根本真言</l>
<lb n="0040c09" ed="T"/><l>或心一字明</l><l>或<note n="0040070" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">業＝樂【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040070"><lem wit="【大】">業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【丙】">樂</rdg></app>心中心</l>
<lb n="0040c10" ed="T"/><l>擿枳王真言</l><l>住定疲極已</l>
<lb n="0040c11" ed="T"/><l>方坐誦讚歎</l><l>陳供及發願</l>
<lb n="0040c12" ed="T"/><l>即<note n="0040071" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">作＝是【明】</note><app n="0040071"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">是</rdg></app>解脫法</l><l>以本法四印</l>
<lb n="0040c13" ed="T"/><l>四處掣開之</l></lg>
<lb n="0040c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0040c1401">心上真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0040c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0040c1501" cb:type="dharani">唵<app type="star" corresp="#0040064"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>薩怛<app type="star" corresp="#0040065"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0040065"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0040072" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惹＝若【明】，入【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0040072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惹＝若【明】，＝入【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0040072"><lem wit="【大】">惹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">若</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">入</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0040065"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二<app type="star" corresp="#0039025"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">合引</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0040c16" ed="T"/>羅麼<note place="inline">引</note>羅<note n="0040073" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">矩＝句【甲】</note><app n="0040073"><lem wit="【大】">矩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">句</rdg></app>嚕<note n="0040074" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合引〕－【甲】</note><app n="0040074"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>馱吽<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0040062"><lem wit="【大】">短</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">短聲</rdg></app></note>發吒<note place="inline">半音</note>目</p>
<pb n="0041a" xml:id="T21.1209.0041a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0041a01" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0041a0101"><l>又以真實王</l><l>四印掣開之</l></lg>
<lb n="0041a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0041a0201">心上真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0041a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0041a0301" cb:type="dharani">唵<app type="star" corresp="#0040064"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>薩怛<app type="star" corresp="#0040065"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0040065"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>吽<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0040062"><lem wit="【大】">短</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">短聲</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0041a04" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT21p0041a0401"><l>聖眾還宮已</l><l>即寶鬘甲拍</l>
<lb n="0041a05" ed="T"/><l>護此常恒身</l><l>四禮五向等</l>
<lb n="0041a06" ed="T"/><l>餘皆同諸教</l><l>降三世瑜伽</l>
<lb n="0041a07" ed="T"/><l>二羽<note n="0041001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝即【甲】</note><app n="0041001"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>當心</l><l>慧手持五<note n="0041002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鈷＝股【甲】＊</note><app n="0041002"><lem wit="【大】">鈷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">股</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0041a08" ed="T"/><l>努臂如下擬</l><l>次箭劍直執</l>
<lb n="0041a09" ed="T"/><l>定上五<app type="star" corresp="#0041002"><lem wit="【大】">鈷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">股</rdg></app><note n="0041003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鉤＝鈴ィ【丙】</note><app n="0041003"><lem wit="【大】">鉤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="variantRemark">鈴</rdg></app></l><l>次弓次執索</l>
<lb n="0041a10" ed="T"/><l>皆直引臂持</l><l>四面正青色</l>
<lb n="0041a11" ed="T"/><l>右黃左綠色</l><l>後紅<note n="0041004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咸＝感【甲】</note><app n="0041004"><lem wit="【大】">咸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">感</rdg></app>忿怒</l>
<lb n="0041a12" ed="T"/><l>自在天王<note n="0041005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妃＝后【丙】</note><app n="0041005"><lem wit="【大】">妃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">后</rdg></app></l><l>為座如前說</l>
<lb n="0041a13" ed="T"/><l>吽迦<note n="0041006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0041006"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app>金剛</l><l>作如是相<note n="0041007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">好＋（降三世金剛真言曰曩謨引羅怛曩二合怛羅二合夜引野曩莫室戰二合拏引縛曰羅二合播引拏曳二摩賀藥乞叉二合細曩引鉢跢曳唵遜婆去𩕳遜婆去吽短疙哩二合恨拏二合疙哩二合恨拏二合吽短疙哩二合恨拏播野吽阿去引曩野斛引婆誐鑁嚩曰囉二合吽發吒）百九字【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0041007"><lem wit="【大】">好</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">好降三世金剛真言曰曩謨引羅怛曩二合怛羅二合夜引野曩莫室戰二合拏引縛曰羅二合播引拏曳二摩賀藥乞叉二合細曩引鉢跢曳唵遜婆去𩕳遜婆去吽短疙哩二合恨拏二合疙哩二合恨拏二合吽短疙哩二合恨拏播野吽阿去引曩野斛引婆誐鑁嚩曰囉二合吽發吒</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0041a14" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0041008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（降三世）＋金【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0041008"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">降三世金</rdg></app><note n="0041009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">剛＋（頂）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0041009"><lem wit="【大】">剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">剛頂</rdg></app>瑜伽<note n="0041010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔降三世〕－【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0041010"><lem wit="【大】">降三世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>成就極深密<note n="0041011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（法）【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0041011"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">門法</rdg></app><note n="0041012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一卷＝終（細註）【明】【乙】</note><note n="0041012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷＝（終）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0041012"><lem wit="【大】">一<note n="0041013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本奧書曰延久六年三月十八日書了高野末葉金剛弟子淨秀本也，乙本奧書曰時貞享四年盂春三十日一校了淨嚴四十九，元祿十六年正月十九日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教，寶永五年十月八日一校了性寂</note>卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><note place="inline">終</note></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
